@startuml
node "User's Computer" {
  [Python Environment]
  [SQLite Database]
  [Terminal / Command Line]
}

package "Momentum Hub Application" {
  [momentum_cli.py] as CLI
  [cli_*.py modules] as CLIModules
  [habit.py] as Habit
  [momentum_db.py] as DB
  [habit_analysis.py] as Analysis
}

[Terminal / Command Line] --> CLI : run python momentum_cli.py
CLI --> CLIModules : import CLI modules
CLIModules --> Habit : create/update habits
CLIModules --> DB : persist data
CLIModules --> Analysis : analyze data

Habit --> DB : business logic
DB --> [SQLite Database] : store data

[Python Environment] --> [momentum_cli.py] : execute
[Python Environment] --> [SQLite Database] : access local DB

note right of [SQLite Database]
  Local file-based database
  No external dependencies
  Data stored in .db file
end note

note right of [Terminal / Command Line]
  Command-line interface
  Interactive menus using questionary
  Colored output with colorama
end note
@enduml
